{"tid":817902,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［中文人入]請教「屈」字意思","createTime":"2018-09-13T16:35:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T18:37:05.000Z","uid":170370,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4f8940caaf62f741338b79c95c7422edbea468","tid":817902,"uid":170370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T16:35:20.000Z","msg":"廣東話「屈」字作為動詞，例如：A屈B做左某件事。<br />\n意思最接近以下邊一個：<br />\n1）A指B做左某件事，而B冇做過。<br />\n2）A指B做左某件事，而B冇做過。A唔知真相，但基於一啲誤會，真心相信B有做。<br />\n3）A指B做左某件事，而B冇做過。A唔知真相，但基於偏見，咬定B有做。<br />\n4）A指B做左某件事，而B冇做過。A知道真相，但故意誣陷B有做。<br />\n<br />\n請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  thanks"},{"pid":"52980b6de9a0605fca10ccd12fdedd281297ce6a","tid":817902,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以一詞多義？"},{"pid":"a31ad9e786d812040a12a130d7ea8ea28f57e430","tid":817902,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"以上皆可能<br />\n<br />\n利申：中文人"},{"pid":"fbc0159f6932df46ed0478c1edfd0a92a3085d33","tid":817902,"uid":195904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T16:52:45.000Z","msg":"4囉傻閪"},{"pid":"2a4aeb6af32cec972e3bcc31fd8d5e88fb70491f","tid":817902,"uid":135278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"4個都係⋯屈左就係屈左<br />\nA知唔知真相/A信唔信B都無關係<br />\n最緊要係B無做 而個指控係由A提出既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647acc2f3972f1800538eecf0e7c99f2692ba20c","tid":817902,"uid":51848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a4aeb6af32cec972e3bcc31fd8d5e88fb70491f","tid":817902,"uid":135278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"4個都係⋯屈左就係屈左<br />\nA知唔知真相/A信唔信B都無關係<br />\n最緊要係B無做 而個指控係由A提出既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T18:37:05.000Z","msg":"正解"}]}